          "message": "Negated condition in `scheduleMemberWelcomeEmailJob` flips scheduling logic: previously the job was scheduled when `processOutbox` was false, now it is scheduled only when `processOutbox` is true, which means the job will never be scheduled on the first call and will be scheduled repeatedly on subsequent calls.",
