          "severity": "high",
          "category": "logic_error",
          "message": "Welcome email condition changed from `labs.isSet('welcomeEmails') && WELCOME_EMAIL_SOURCES.includes(source)` to `config.get('memberWelcomeEmailTestInbox') || WELCOME_EMAIL_SOURCES.includes(source)`. The new OR logic means that if `memberWelcomeEmailTestInbox` is set to any truthy value, welcome emails are sent for *all* sources, not just the allowed ones, which can cause unintended email sending for sources like 'import' or 'admin'.",
